      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>春节促销页面</title>\n<style>\n  body {\n    margin: 0;\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    background-color: #F4F4F5;\n    color: #4E342E;\n  }\n  header {\n    background-color: #C62828;\n    color: #FFFFFF;\n    padding: 20px;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n  }\n  header h1 {\n    margin: 0;\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n  }\n  nav a {\n    color: #FFD54F;\n    margin-left: 15px;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    font-weight: bold;\n  }\n  #promotion-banner {\n    background-color: #FFD54F;\n    color: #4E342E;\n    padding: 15px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  #promotion-banner div {\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n    font-weight: bold;\n  }\n  main {\n    padding: 20px;\n    text-align: center;\n    background-color: #FFFFFF;\n  }\n  main img {\n    max-width: 100%;\n    height: auto;\n  }\n  main h2 {\n    color: #C62828;\n    margin-top: 15px;\n  }\n  #price-info {\n    padding: 15px;\n    background-color: #F4F4F5;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  #price-info span:first-child {\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    color: #C62828;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    margin-right: 10px;\n  }\n  #price-info span:last-child {\n    text-decoration: line-through;\n    color: #4E342E;\n  }\n  #purchase-channel {\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 20px;\n    background-color: #FFFFFF;\n  }\n  #purchase-channel input {\n    width: 50px;\n    padding: 5px;\n    margin-right: 10px;\n  }\n  #purchase-channel button {\n    padding: 10px 15px;\n    margin: 5px;\n    border: none;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-weight: bold;\n  }\n  #purchase-channel button:first-of-type {\n    background-color: #C62828;\n    color: #FFFFFF;\n  }\n  #purchase-channel button:last-of-type {\n    background-color: #FFD54F;\n    color: #4E342E;\n  }\n  #category-section {\n    padding: 20px;\n    background-color: #F4F4F5;\n  }\n  #category-section h3 {\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n    color: #C62828;\n  }\n  #category-section ul {\n    list-style: none;\n    padding: 0;\n  }\n  #category-section li {\n    background-color: #FFFFFF;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n    padding: 10px;\n    border: 1px solid #DDD;\n  }\n  #shopping-cart {\n    padding: 20px;\n    background-color: #FFFFFF;\n  }\n  #shopping-cart h3 {\n    color: #C62828;\n  }\n  #shopping-cart ul {\n    list-style: none;\n    padding: 0;\n  }\n  #shopping-cart li {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #DDD;\n    padding: 8px 0;\n  }\n  footer {\n    background-color: #C62828;\n    color: #FFFFFF;\n    padding: 15px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  footer nav a {\n    color: #FFD54F;\n    margin: 0 10px;\n    text-decoration: none;\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<header id=\"site-header\">\n  <h1>新春特惠</h1>\n  <nav>\n    <a href=\"#\">首页</a>\n    <a href=\"#\">分类</a>\n    <a href=\"#\">购物车</a>\n  </nav>\n</header>\n\n<section id=\"promotion-banner\">\n  <div>限时抢购：剩余2天5小时</div>\n  <p>领取春节满减优惠券，抢年货福利</p>\n</section>\n\n<main id=\"product-overview\">\n  <img src=\"product.jpg\" alt=\"春节特色礼盒\">\n  <h2>春节特色礼盒 - 美味团圆</h2>\n  <p>多种口味，精美包装，送礼佳品</p>\n</main>\n\n<section id=\"price-info\">\n  <span>￥199</span>\n  <span>￥299</span>\n  <p>立省￥100，优惠力度空前</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"purchase-channel\">\n  <input type=\"number\" min=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n  <button>立即购买</button>\n  <button>加入购物车</button>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"category-section\">\n  <h3>更多年货零食</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li>坚果礼盒</li>\n    <li>糖果大礼包</li>\n    <li>茶叶礼盒</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<aside id=\"shopping-cart\">\n  <h3>购物车</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><span>春节特色礼盒 x1</span> <button>删除</button></li>\n    <li><span>坚果礼盒 x2</span> <button>删除</button></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>共计 ￥399 | 已存储在本地</p>\n</aside>\n\n<footer id=\"site-footer\">\n  <p>© 2024 春节快乐，阖家幸福</p>\n  <nav>\n    <a href=\"#\">客服</a>\n    <a href=\"#\">退换政策</a>\n  </nav>\n</footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
